To build and install JasPer do the following:

In what follows, let $SOURCE_DIR denote the top-level directory of the JasPer
software source tree.

1) Select an empty or new directory to use for building the software.
Let $BUILD_DIR denote this directory.

2) Run cmake:
cmake -H$SOURCE_DIR -B$BUILD_DIR

3) Build the code:
cd $BUILD_DIR

4) Build the code
make clean all

5) Run test suite:
make test

6) Install the software:
make install

